<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>EU Relay Servers – M45-Science</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link href="icon.png" rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" />

  <style>
    /* -----------------------------------
       CSS Variables (customize as needed)
    ----------------------------------- */
    :root {
      --bg-gradient-start: #111111;
      --bg-gradient-end: #2a2a2a;
      --header-bg: #1b1b1b;
      --text-color: #eeeeee;
      --secondary-text-color: #bbbbbb;
      --accent-color-1: #4fc3f7;
      /* First accent color */
      --accent-color-2: #2196f3;
      /* Second accent color for gradient */
      --panel-bg: #222222;
      --panel-hover-bg: #333333;
      --server-bg: #333333;
      --server-hover-bg: #444444;
      --server-hover-shadow: rgba(79, 195, 247, 0.4);
      --box-shadow-base: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      --box-shadow-hover: 0 6px 14px var(--server-hover-shadow);
    }

    /* ------------------
       Global Base Styles
    ------------------ */
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html,
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-gradient-start), var(--bg-gradient-end));
      color: var(--text-color);
      padding-bottom: 400px;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--accent-color-1);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* -----------
       Header Area
    ------------ */
    header {
      background-color: var(--header-bg);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    }

    header a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    header img {
      width: 120px;
      height: auto;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin: 10px 0 5px;
      /* Gradient text effect */
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent-color-1), var(--accent-color-2));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    header h2 {
      color: var(--secondary-text-color);
      font-weight: normal;
      font-style: italic;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* ---------------
       Main Layout
    ---------------- */
    .layout {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 30px;
      max-width: 1500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .info-panel,
    .Relay-panel {
      flex: 1 1 100%;
      max-width: 1000px;
      background-color: var(--panel-bg);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .info-panel h2,
    .Relay-panel h2,
    .connect-panel-wrapper h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--accent-color-1);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-color-1);
      display: inline-block;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .info-panel ul,
    .Relay-panel ul {
      text-align: left;
      max-width: 1500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    /* ----------------------
       Connect Panel & Tiles
    ----------------------- */
    .connect-panel-wrapper {
      flex: 1 1 100%;
      max-width: 1500px;
      background-color: var(--panel-bg);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .connect-panel {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .server-link {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    .server {
      background-color: var(--server-bg);
      padding: 10px;
      min-width: 150px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-base);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .server:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-hover);
      background-color:var(--server-hover-bg);
    }

    .server h3 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--secondary-text-color);
    }

    .server-address {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #aaa;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      word-wrap: break-word;
    }

    .connect-label {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #444;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: #ccc;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 5px;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .server:hover .connect-label {
      background-color: var(--accent-color-1);
      color: #000;
      box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--accent-color-1);
    }

    /* Minor Note about Non-Steam */
    .minor-note {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--secondary-text-color);
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .server-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      max-width: 1500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .server {
      background-color: var(--server-bg);
      width: 300px;
      min-height: 120px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.2rem;
    }

    .server:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    }

    .server h3 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-color);
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .server h4 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-color);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

.server a {
  background-color: var(--accent-color-1);
  padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
  border-radius: 6px;
  color: #000; /* for better contrast on cyan */
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: bold;
  transition: background-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
}

.server a:hover {
  background-color: var(--accent-color-2);
  color: #fff;
}
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <a href="https://m45sci.xyz/">
      <img src="https://m45sci.xyz/m45-2024b-128.png" alt="M45-Science Logo" />
      <h1>M45-Science</h1>
      <h2>EU Relay Portal</h2>
    </a>
  </header>

  <!-- Content Layout -->
  <div class="layout">
    <!-- Intro / Info Panel -->
    <div class="info-panel">
      <h2>Improve Your Connection from Europe</h2>
      <p>
        If you're playing Factorio from Europe and experiencing lag, stuttering, or disconnects
        on M45-Science servers, our EU Relay system can help smooth out your connection.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our main <strong>Factorio servers</strong> are hosted in <strong>Michigan, USA</strong>
        (near Chicago and the Great Lakes) by <strong>incx</strong>.
        The <strong>EU Relay servers</strong> are located in <strong>Nuremberg, Germany</strong>,
        hosted by <strong>Hetzner</strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        This relay routes your traffic through a stable TCP tunnel from Europe to the US, reducing:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Packet loss</li>
        <li>Transatlantic latency spikes</li>
        <li>Disconnections caused by poor ISP routing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Connect Panel -->
    <div class="connect-panel-wrapper">
      <h2>Click a Relay to Join</h2>
      <p>Select one of the servers below to launch Factorio via an EU relay.</p>
      <div class="server-list">
    {{range .Servers}}
      <div class="server">
        <h3>{{.Name}}</h3>
        <h4>{{.Addr}}:{{.Port}}</h4>
        <a href="steam://run/427520//--mp-connect%20{{.Addr}}:{{.Port}}/">Connect</a>
      </div>
    {{end}}
  </div>

      <!-- Minor Note about Non-Steam -->
      <div class="minor-note">
        <p>
          <strong>Note:</strong> If you prefer to connect without Steam, copy the address
          (e.g. <code>eu.m45sci.xyz:20000</code>) and use <em>Multiplayer → Connect to address</em> in Factorio.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Relay Software Panel -->
    <div class="Relay-panel">
      <h2 id="downloads" >Optional Relay Software</h2>
      <p>
        You can also run our optional <strong>Relay software</strong> on your computer.
        Unlike the EU relay links above, it creates a direct tunnel from your PC
        to the M45-Science servers in Michigan.
      </p>
      <p>This can help if you encounter:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>WiFi instability</li>
        <li>CGNAT or router challenges</li>
        <li>Unusual ISP routing</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">Downloads</h3>
      <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1rem 0;">
      {{/* Disable 
        <li>• <a href="M45-Relay-Client-Windows.zip">M45-Relay-Client-Windows.zip</a></li>
        <li>• <a href="M45-Relay-Client-Linux.zip">M45-Relay-Client-Linux.zip</a></li>
        <li>• <a href="M45-Relay-Client-Mac.zip">M45-Relay-Client-Mac.zip</a> (Universal Apple/Intel)</li>
        */}}
        (Work in progress)
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>